name: Mutabbal
description: Pureed Chickpeas with tahini, lemon juice and a touch of garlic.

name: Hummus
description: Chargrilled aubergine blended with tahini and lemon juice topped with fresh pomegranate seeds.

name: Musabbaha
description: Traditional palestinian mixture of broad beans and chickpeas with touch of garlic and tahina sauce. Seasoned with special mixture of sweet and chilly peppers  and olive oil.

name: Foul Mudammas
description: Broad beans paste with garlic and olive oil.

name: Waraq Enab
description: Popular middle eastern appetizer served in Palestinian way: known by it’s tiny size our wine leaves are rich in flavor of herbs, pomegranate seeds and pomegranate syrup.

name: Fried Kubba
description: Crispy outside and jucy inside our Kubba will let you fall in love with it’s taste.

name: Falafel
description: Deep fried balls of chickpeas and favs beans mixture enriched with special spices and fresh herbs.

name: Galayet Bandora
description: Tomato stew cooked of hand-picked tomatoes, herbs and spices, topped with  chilly pepper (optional).

name: Galayet Bandora with Meat
description: Tomato stew cooked of hand-picked tomatoes, herbs and spices, topped with  chilly pepper (optional).
